### 1. Financial Agent (Port 9000)
### Health check
GET http://localhost:9000/health

### News query
POST http://localhost:9000/api/news
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "Summarize the latest market news regarding the rupee falling against dollar and also currency exchange rate of dollar and rupee.",
  "reset": true
}

### 2. Risk Pipeline (Port 8000)
### Safety Check
POST http://localhost:8000/v1/is-safe
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "text": "This is a guaranteed 20% daily return investment opportunity."
}

### 3. Production Check
POST https://financial-agent-deploy-1.onrender.com/api/news
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "Give me the top crypto headlines today.",
  "reset": true
}

